Lisa O'Hare https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lisa_O%27Hare 0 Lisa O'Hare began her career as an English stage actress who has played Eliza Doolittle in My Fair Lady and the title character of Mary Poppins on the West End and UK stage. She more recently has appeared in several prime-time American television shows on TNT, ABC and NBC. She most recently starred on Broadway in the new musical, A Gentleman's Guide to Love and Murder.
